high_descs: Walk over to the microwave on the counter behind you and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost upper cabinet door and take the wooden cup out of the cabinet, then close the cabinet.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the wall, turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the wooden cup inside then close the fridge, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled wooden cup then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then hang a left and walk over to the door, turn right and walk up to the microwave then look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost upper cabinet door and put the chilled wooden cup inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wooden cup in an upper cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the microwave.
Take the yellow cup out of the top left cabinet.
Turn around and walk ahead, veering left to the fridge.
Place the cup on the top shelf of the bottom part of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and veer right, back the the microwave on the counter.
Place the cup in the top left cabinet, on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cup in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to face the cabinet above the microwave.
Take the gold cup from the cabinet.
Turn right to walk across the room to the fridge.
Chill the gold cup in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk back towards the microwave.
Put the gold cup back in the cabinet above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill a gold cup in the fridge to put back in the cabinet above the microwave.
